    dc:description "FIG. 4. Dorsal views of the rostrum of Marmosops invictus (A, USNM 306386) and M. fuscatus (B, FMNH 22174), illustrating taxonomic differences in nasal width. Abbreviations: fro, frontal; max, maxillary; nas, nasal." ;
